quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,65,"Aadfoͻ nso wͻn nua Huud kͻͻ wͻn hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, (efrisε) monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Enti monnnsuro Nyankopͻn na monnyε ahwεyie?”"
  7,66,"Nhemfo {anaa mpanimfoͻ} boniayεfoͻ a εwͻ nenkorͻfoͻ no mu no kaa sε: “Nokorε, yehu wo sε wo wͻ agyimisεm mu na yε’dwen sε woka nkontompofoͻ no ho"
  7,67,"Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, εnyε gyimii na m’agyimi, na mmom meyε Ɔsomafoͻ fri Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ “"
  7,68,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro na merebɔ akyerε mo, na meyε ofutufo pa nokwafoͻ ma mo"
  7,69,"Anaasε εyε mo nwanwa sε Afutusεm fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ nam mo mu nipa bi so aba mo hͻ sε ͻmεbͻ mo kͻkͻ? Monkae εberε a Ɔyεε mo ananmusifoͻ wͻ Noa nkorͻfoͻ no akyi, na Ɔmaa mo nkͻsoͻ wͻ abͻdeε (a atwa moho ahyia) no mu. Enti monkae Nyankopͻn adom, sεdeε mobedi nkonim"
  7,70,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Wobaa yεn hͻ sεdeε yεbεsom Nyankopͻn nko ara, na yεbegyae deε na y’agyanom som? Ɛneε fa deε worehyε yεn ho bͻ no bra, sε woka nokwafoͻ no ho ampa a”"
  7,71,"Ɔkaa sε: “Nokorε asotwee ne abufuo fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba mo so. Moregye me akyinnye wͻ (abosom) din a mo ne moagya nom atotoͻ no ho, abrɛ a Nyankopͻn nsianee tumi biara wɔ ho? Eneɛ montwεn, na meka mo ne wͻn a wͻ’retwεn no ho"
  7,72,Enti Yε’de ahummͻborͻ a efiri Yεn hͻ no gyee no ne wͻn a wͻ’ka ne ho no nkwa. Na Yε’tͻree wͻn a wͻ’faa Yεn Nsεm no atorͻsεm no ase. Na (saa nkorͻfoͻ no) nyε agyidiefoͻ